  "name": "Deploy - Shopify Connector",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"deploy-shopify-connector\">Deploy - Shopify Connector</h1>\n<p><span><span>This article explains how to deploy a Shopify Connector once a signed contract has been received and paid for:</span></span></p>\n<p><span>Enable Shopify Connector</span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (58).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powboEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powboEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powboEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powboEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powboEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powboEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powboEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powboEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Login to <a href=\"\">MGMT</a></p>\n<p>2. Navigate to <strong>BackOffice &gt; BO Site List</strong></p>\n<p>3. Filter by company name in <strong>Admin Link</strong></p>\n<p>4. Click on <span><strong>Edit</strong></span> and select <strong>Basic</strong> from the dropdown options under <strong>Shopify License</strong></p>\n<p>5. Select<strong> <span>Update</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span>Enable Multiple Shopify Connectors</span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (59).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powVgEAI.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powVgEAI.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powVgEAI.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powVgEAI.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powVgEAI.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powVgEAI.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powVgEAI.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powVgEAI.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. If client has purchased more than 1 Connector then go to <strong>Shopify &gt; Shopify Site List</strong></p>\n<p>2. Filter by company name in <strong>Admin Link</strong></p>\n<p>3. Clink on <strong><span>Edit</span></strong> and select the relevant number of connectors under <strong>Licensed Stores </strong></p>\n<p>4. Select <strong><span>Update</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span>Zendesk - Sending the email </span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (60).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfzEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfzEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfzEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfzEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfzEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfzEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfzEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powfzEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Add a new ticket</p>\n<p>2. Add the email address for the contact on the solutions agreement</p>\n<p>3. Select the macro <strong>Implementation &gt; Shopify BYO: Getting Started</strong></p>\n<p>5. Submit the ticket as Solved</p>",
